node.text:
Answering lots of questions I’ve been receiving about my new weekly newsletters.
Link for this set- https://bit.ly/weeklynewsletters

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maribel-Learning in Wonderland on July 29, 2021.

node.text: Anyone pick up these cute rulers from the 🎯 dollar spot? I made these tags go with them! I’m sending them out to everyone signed up for my newsletter this weekend. Link in profile to sign up- https://bit.ly/wonderlandmail

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maribel-Learning in Wonderland on July 29, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Getting lots of requests for the link to these editable water bottle labels. We’re in Arizona and I found that so many of the families appreciated having water there for them. I’m linking them for you in my profile: http://bit.ly/waterlabels

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maribel-Learning in Wonderland on July 28, 2021. StORY eLements PRINTABLE 2020- PAPER SAVING INTERACTIVE FLIPBOOK Memory Book Primary Class CERTIFICATE TION >>>STRY eLements CHARACTERS 3 NG MIDDLE END BEGINNING'.

node.text:
New Bundle ✨60% OFF✨ I’ve been asked if I could create a bilingual (English & Spanish) bundle for a while. I was waiting until I had enough resources to create a good bundle and I’m happy to say that it’s here!

This bundle will be added to in the future and the price will grow accordingly.

You can grab it 60% off for the next 24 hours. Link in profile: https://bit.ly/bilingualbundle

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Maribel-Learning in Wonderland on July 27, 2021.

node.text: These labels are done and I’m obsessed!😍 Those of you who purchased through the pre-sale, please go download now! I’m leaving them on sale for the next 24 hours! Link in bio- https://bit.ly/teachercartlabels

node.text: On sale! 🚨 I’ve had requests for 10 drawer cart labels for a long time and I decided to tackle that project this summer. I picked up a couple of carts to work with and I’m in love with how they both turned out! I’m leaving this pre-sale discount on until the set is complete. It should be done tonight or tomorrow morning! Link in profile- https://bit.ly/teachercartlabels

node.text:
Look at all these goodies I just found at @michaelsstores! #ad I always had my students make a self portrait at the beginning of the year, but how fun would it be for them to create their own little person that represents them?

I love how their new foam shape people include a variety of skin tones so that children can make a person that looks like them!

You can find everything you need to create these at @michaelsstores 😍
#MakeItWithMichaels
